Class SObjectWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sforce.soap.partner.sobject.SObject
      • com.knowledgebin.kb.SObjectWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, org.apache.axis.encoding.AnyContentType

    public class SObjectWrapper
extends com.sforce.soap.partner.sobject.SObject
    This class provides a easier to use getStringValue function. CMA180820 #51751 And now implements some of the function of the SF WSC (e.g. setField and getStringValue) CMA181027 #53233 Added empty constructor and refactored to use this class methods to access the wrapped SObject CMA190228 #56589 Expanded to cover new SObject definition in version 42.0 of the sforce-soap-partner.jar

        public void setField(String name,
